# 🎓 Student Management Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview

The **Student Management Dashboard** is a web-based application designed to simplify and streamline the management of student data 
for educational institutions. This dashboard allows administrators, teachers, and staff to manage student profiles, academic records,
attendance, and performance insights from a centralized and user-friendly interface.


## ✨ Features

* ✅ Add, view, edit, and delete student records
* 📚 Manage course and subject enrollments
* 📊 Track student grades and academic performance
* 🕒 Record and view attendance logs
* 🔍 Search and filter students by class, grade, or name
* 📈 Interactive dashboard for quick insights
* 🧑‍🏫 Role-based access control (Admin, Teacher, Student)

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

Frontend: HTML, CSS, Js
Tools: VS Code, Git, GitHub




## ✅ Future Improvements

* Add notifications or alert system
* Integration with email/SMS API for updates
* Export reports in PDF/Excel formats
* Mobile responsiveness and PWA features



